name: Jet Set Fly
description:
This time you will have to master jumping and jetpacking trough endless obstacles coming your way. How long can you survive?

If you managed to get 4 coins without touching the ground you get a shield, this will be vital for your survival! Be careful with the grey coins, they will break your combo and send you down to ground!

Controls --------------------------------------------------
Any button: Up/down/left/right//Z/X

- Hold to charge your jump and release to jump
- In air: Hold the button to use your jetpack

--------------------------------------------------

Good luck and stay awesome!

/ Elastiskalinjen
